forecastday.title: Tuesday

forecastday.title: Wednesday

forecastday.title: Wednesday Night
forecastday.fcttext: Rain and snow in the evening becoming partly cloudy late. Low 24F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of snow 80%. Snow accumulations less than one inch.
forecastday.fcttext_metric: Snow in the evening will give way to partly cloudy conditions overnight. Low near -5C. Winds SSW at 10 to 15 km/h. Chance of snow 80%. Snow accumulations less than 2cm.
